Name: PaWz 100 Pcs 60x60cm Charcoal Pet Puppy Dog Toilet Training Pads Ultra Absorbent
Description:
DESCRIPTION

Our dog pads are highly absorbent and won't leak or spread. They are made with Flash-Dry technology that instantly turns liquid into a gel, preventing leaks that can damage your floor or carpet. These Dog Pads instantly eliminate odors and contains a fresh lavender scent for lasting freshness.

  • Flash-dry technology instantly turns liquid into gel
  • Won't spread and won't leak
  • Helps to protect your floor and carpet
  • Fresh Lavender Scent
  • Eliminates odors
  • Transforms bad smells into a pleasant scent
  • Keeps your home smelling clean
  • Black potty pads, so your pets mess stays discrete and you never see a yellow stain on a white puppy pad in your home
  • Odor Elimination with carbon technology for all-day use to ensure your home stays fresh
  • Ultra Absorbent

How to use a dog pad:
Unfold and place the pad, plastic side down, in a confined area, away from your dog's bed and food.
Place your dog on the pad several times so he can smell the pad and get used to it.
While your dog is eliminating on the pad, use a phrase like "go potty" so that eventually you can use the command and your dog will understand what it means.  
Immediately after the dog eliminates on the pad, reward him with praise and a treat.
If your dog has an accident, bring him back to the pad immediately. Continue bringing your dog back to the pad to reinforce that this is the place to go potty.
Dispose of soiled pads and replace as needed.To complete house training, gradually move the pad closer to the door and finally outside.

SPECIFICATION
  • Material: Non-woven fabric
  • Size: 60x60cm
  • Quantity:100pcs
PACKAGE CONTENTS
  • 100x Puppy Training Pads

Name: Automatic Chicken Feeder Self Open Poultry Alumnium Treadle 10KG Capacity Outdoor
Description:
DESCRIPTION

Experiencing troubled feeding time? Eliminate all the chicken feeding troubles with our innovative Automatic Chicken Feeder. Save your precious time and energy. Designed to feed your adorable chickens in timed intervals. Set it up anywhere as required, fill the container with chicken feed, and your work is done. It will perform the crucial feeding process without any delay. It eases your everyday feeding tasks with minimal effort.  A minimal weight equivalent to a regular-sized chicken is required for the automatic feeder to start processing. This creative feature keeps other trespassers such as wild birds, rats, and mice from accessing food container. No more wastage of chicken feed.

Made from high-quality galvanized iron. A special rust-proof galvanized coating is provided on the entire body to provide active resistance towards the water. Effectively keeps all the food inside clean and fresh. A solid and durable construction helps withstand long term and regular use. Equipped with very large-sized container to hold up to 12.5L of feed. To access the food container a minimum of 500g weight is required. Very easy to assemble with simple instructions. Economic and very low on maintenance.

Feeding your chicken strategically and efficiently. A perfect and ideal choice.

Key Features:

  • Effective feed cost saver
  • 0.5kg Auto lid opening
  • Rust-proof galvanized steel
  • Keeps feed clean and fresh
  • Smooth edges and operation
  • Non-slip pedal
  • Large capacity
  • Waterproof and durable
  • Easy to assemble and low maintenance
  • Suitable for most bantams
  • Trespasser prevention (Birds, rats, mice etc)

  • Material:Galvanized steel

  • Thickness:0.8mm
  • Weight 2.7kg

  • Colour: Silver

DESCRIPTION

Take your little one for a fun ride with our Pet Stroller. It provides your pet with a safe and secure space to lounge, to enjoy the nature, or to simply be themselves. It comes with a meshed front to give your furry friend a comprehensive view of the surroundings all while reclining in style. Great way to socialize your pet with less exposure to risks such as harmful terrain, irregular weather, flying insects, or any other non-friendly pets they might encounter. Going through uneven surface? Not a worry, with its modern spring shock absorption it will ensure a smoother experience. Featuring 6 wheels for a stress-free and easy-going ride. It comprises of removable and washable pads, easy for you to keep it neat and tidy all the time. After all the walk if you feel like taking a break, just lock the wheels up and park the stroller safely, it’s that simple!

A pet to cater, a nature to feel, a moment to remember. Start your journey! Order your stroller now.

Description:
Our Natural Wild Berry shampoo and conditioner for Westies and other breeds with white coats or lighter coloured coat.

Our unique  Berry Fruit Sorbet fragrance is a natural fruit extract that gives a bold, long-lasting freshness to the coat.

Specifically formulated for more advanced whitening this shampoo contains a stain removing agent and is blue in appearance, which whitens white coats and assists in reducing dirty stains and unsightly stains caused from tear, urine and licking.

While whitening the coat, it also provides a deep cleanse to the coat and skin and leaves no blue/grey residue.

Rosemary essential oil is used to provide anti-bacterial, wound healing, antiseptic and toning effects.

Simply empty pool water through convenient drain valve after some splashing time. Alternative use as a bathtub to give a pet a warm nice bath. Dry under sunshade, then fold it up and pack quickly.

Your dog may sleep anywhere but they will be far happier having a space to call their own. This elevated dog bed is as stylish as your own bed. Such luxury. Wow.

Name: PaWz Pet Travel Carrier Kennel Folding Soft Sided Dog Crate For Car Cage Large L
Description:
DESCRIPTION

Got friends coming over who are allergic to your fluffball. Clean your place up and put Mr Kittens away in your soft kennel for the visit. When they have left let him roam free.

Fold it for easy storage. When you need to use your dog crate just lift the sides up and connect the tubes. You are ready to go in 30 seconds. Take your cat with you on a family trip or take your dog to the vet.

Going camping is one of life’s great joys. Take your dog along with you in their soft sided dog crate. Let them roam around the campsite and then keep them safe at night.

Accidents happen but they won’t ruin your new soft kennel. Take the cushion cover off and throw it in the washing machine. Hand wash everything else. Very quick and easy to clean.

You have your dog in their new soft dog crate. How do you get them into your car? Just lift them up with the handles on the top. Easy as cake.

  • Durable and tough

Name: Dog Cat Pet Hair Dryer Grooming Blow Speed Hairdryer Blower Heater Blaster 2800W
Description:
DESCRIPTION

Dogs love to jump and play in everything. You have washed your dog yet again from their mud bath! At least this time you can dry them off quickly. A happy dog is a dry and clean dog.

No more wet dog smell around the house. Clean your fluffy dog then dry them straight away with your new dog hair dryer. Faster drying means a healthier dog particularly for long-haired breeds.

It is almost cross between a vacuum cleaner and a blow dryer. Just select the right setting and point the nozzle at your pet’s fur. Keep moving the nozzle over your pet until they are dried. Easy.

Your dog will soon learn to love their pet blow dryer. Introduce it to them slowly and start at a lower temperature and speed. Get them used to it over a few sessions. Start slow but dry fast.

We are not saying this is perfect to dry children with. We would never say that. If you happened to have a wet child and wanted them dry fast. Well this pet hair dryer does a great job of drying.

DESCRIPTION

Trained your cat to use a litter box? Superb. That litter still gets kicked everywhere? Sadness. Your new kitty litter box keeps everything inside the box. The perforated roof knocks more litter from their paws.

Do you close the door when you go to the toilet? Cats desire privacy too. Your cat’s litter box enclosure gives them a sense of security and safety. They enter through the bottom and leave through the top.

Use the bonus scoop to lift out any kitty waste products. If the cat litter tray box is getting a bit funky just empty all the cat litter and give it a scrub. Let it dry then you are good to use again.

Cats love to test out many items in your home. Luckily for you this is tested to stop cats destroying it. They can get in and out thousands of times. Not suitable for super chonkers cats though.

The lid to your cat litter box furniture clips down solidly. If you want to move it somewhere else the integrated handles will be a godsend.
